tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE StatisticalAnalysis (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    measurement_id INT,
    outcome VARCHAR(50),
    analysis_result FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (measurement_id) REFERENCES QuantumMeasurements(id)
);

CREATE TABLE statistical_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    measurement_id INT,
    analysis_type VARCHAR,
    analysis_result VARCHAR,
    analysis_time TIMESTAMP
);
